WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:15.640
So the timeline I'm going to tell you the detail of what the Lord showed me when he came to me as a massive, fiery light, and the light was so bright.

00:00:15.640 --> 00:00:20.667
It literally felt like my spiritual eyes—my whole body—was melting.

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:29.840
I literally said, "Lord, if you don't take and dim the light down and do something, I feel like it's going to kill me, like it's going to burn me up.

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:34.199
" And all of a sudden, because he knew it, he was so intense.

00:00:34.199 --> 00:00:39.222
And I'm telling you, in any intensity, I've never seen anything like this before in my life.

00:00:39.222 --> 00:00:43.138
He took something and he shielded himself.

00:00:44.271 --> 00:00:57.952
It was like a shield, and all of the light that was shining upon my face where it felt like it was blinding me, it came out the side of the shield.

00:00:57.952 --> 00:01:04.895
The light was still going, but it was being shaded and I could see up in it.

00:01:06.470 --> 00:01:16.799
And all of a sudden, a massive dove comes out of it with its wings flapping and an olive branch.

00:01:17.423 --> 00:01:22.764
It came over the top of me and the glory of the Lord filled me.

00:01:26.084 --> 00:01:42.284
And all of a sudden he said, "Brandon, I want to show you the time frame of humanity from the beginning of creation to where we are right now.

00:01:42.284 --> 00:01:50.994
" And he showed me a thin line; it looked like a thread that went through the spans of humanity.

00:01:50.994 --> 00:01:54.020
It went from the beginning all the way to where we are.

00:01:56.027 --> 00:01:56.240
He divided it by thousand-year increments.

00:01:56.780 --> 00:02:08.080
It went 1,000 years, 2,000 years, 3,000 years, 4,000 years, 5,000 years, 6,000 years, and that's where we were.

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:12.366
And then he divided it again into these little blocks.

00:02:12.366 --> 00:02:22.053
So you could take a piece of paper and divide it out into a thousand, and then he divided in between those thousands by hundreds, and then he divided it by tens.

00:02:22.053 --> 00:02:30.000
So for each year, I could see faces.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:53.386
But I just want to say this: from the beginning of time, the dead in Christ—all of the believers that are in the dirt—it looked to me like there were millions of them.

00:02:54.968 --> 00:03:00.680
I could see their bones in the first couple layers of soil around the whole earth.

00:03:08.103 --> 00:03:12.634
There were skulls, hands, and legs; the bones of the believers were still in the dirt like fossilized remains.

00:03:13.099 --> 00:03:21.337
And they were looking in the spirit realm up toward the Father.

00:03:23.423 --> 00:03:30.286
The bones were a representation.

00:03:30.286 --> 00:03:34.231
I know "to be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord," that's what the Bible says.

00:03:34.231 --> 00:03:42.857
But it was like they were looking up in the spirit realm waiting for the "dead in Christ will rise first.

00:03:42.857 --> 00:03:54.720
" And I could see the anticipation in the earth waiting for the Son of Man to come at the rapture of the church, waiting for the coming of the Lord.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:59.840
The ground was anticipating.

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:04.760
The bones were anticipating, kind of like "Can these bones live?

00:04:04.760 --> 00:04:08.933
" like it talks about in the Bible.

00:04:08.933 --> 00:04:21.560
The bones were anticipating the glory, and there was an atmosphere of acceleration and excitement in the bones.

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:25.232
I don't know how; it's just what I saw.

00:04:25.232 --> 00:04:29.249
So he said, "I want to—" and this was something I did not want to skip.

00:04:29.249 --> 00:04:36.220
That was so important for you all to hear this: the dead in Christ are going to rise first and we are going to be all caught up with him.

00:04:36.220 --> 00:04:40.720
Watch what is about to happen, folks.

00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:44.453
I am so excited about it.

00:04:44.453 --> 00:04:46.447
Jesus is coming!

00:04:46.447 --> 00:04:47.907
It's so exciting.

00:04:48.393 --> 00:04:53.549
People have talked about this for generations and we're right there.

00:04:53.549 --> 00:05:03.393
The Lord even told me, "Brandon, I told you there will be a generation that will not taste death and you are that generation.

00:05:03.393 --> 00:05:10.280
You will be that generation that does not taste death.

00:05:10.280 --> 00:05:10.789
" Wow.

00:05:10.789 --> 00:05:11.806
That's you!

00:05:11.806 --> 00:05:13.331
You're still here.

00:05:13.331 --> 00:05:14.920
I believe there's a remnant of you.

00:05:14.920 --> 00:05:23.280
I know there's probably some elderly people that'll probably go home, but I'm telling you, there is a generation that will not taste death.

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:26.380
We will be the ones that are caught up.

00:05:26.380 --> 00:05:27.307
Glory to God!

00:05:27.307 --> 00:05:33.960
And we will see the soon return of our King.

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:44.978
So whenever he took me on the timeline and he took me by year, it was like he could fast forward it on a DVD player or a VCR.

00:05:44.978 --> 00:05:58.933
I know people don't use VCRs now, but like a recorder where you could speed it up, and I could see the years panning out, moving really fast in front of my face like building Legos.

00:06:03.300 --> 00:06:07.293
In each one, I could see the faces of the people that were ruling in that time going back.

00:06:07.293 --> 00:06:11.967
But he starts it out speaking the world into existence.

00:06:11.967 --> 00:06:22.000
And whenever he spoke the earth, I saw the earth come right before me like a ball of clay.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:28.971
A massive brown ball of clay came right in front of me whenever he spoke it into existence.

00:06:28.971 --> 00:06:34.319
And it was without form and void, right?

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:36.259
And darkness was on the face of the deep.

00:06:36.259 --> 00:06:39.297
It all happened right in front of my face.

00:06:39.297 --> 00:06:42.530
And he's allowing me to see it in the timeline.

00:06:42.530 --> 00:06:44.630
And it's a ball of clay.

00:06:44.630 --> 00:06:49.466
It was a massive brown and red ball of clay.

00:06:49.466 --> 00:06:53.580
And when he spoke to it, it started to form.

00:06:53.580 --> 00:06:56.347
But there were no continents.

00:06:56.347 --> 00:07:04.880
It was all one big landmass in one area.

00:07:04.880 --> 00:07:12.880
There wasn't like South America, North America, Asia, and all this; it was just one big thing.

00:07:12.880 --> 00:07:26.039
And I don't know how it all was divided, whether it was Noah's flood or whatever—which I believe was Noah's flood that caused all this land to be divided and to create different continents.

00:07:26.404 --> 00:07:32.936
But when it first started, it was a garden—a massive garden area.

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:40.336
So then he takes me to the garden and I see Adam and he is ripped.

00:07:40.336 --> 00:07:44.610
He is not a plump looking dude like me.

00:07:44.610 --> 00:07:47.200
I'm still working on it.

00:07:47.760 --> 00:07:54.008
He has muscles and he has a black-looking beard and he's olive-skinned.

00:07:54.933 --> 00:08:00.684
I only saw his backside with the glory around him.

00:08:00.684 --> 00:08:06.560
He had no clothes on in the natural; he had a glory around him.

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:15.129
But he had black hair and it went into his beard, and his black beard was perfect.

00:08:20.493 --> 00:08:22.605
The way he looked was amazing.

00:08:22.605 --> 00:08:23.825
His arms were ripped.

00:08:23.825 --> 00:08:32.080
He did not look deteriorated like how we look worn down.

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:34.399
A lot of people's bodies look worn down.

00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:36.075
His body was not dead.

00:08:36.075 --> 00:08:37.535
There was no death.

00:08:37.535 --> 00:08:40.719
So he had no death around him.

00:08:40.719 --> 00:08:44.640
His body was fit and he looked good.

00:08:44.640 --> 00:08:54.826
Like seriously, there was no decay until—and I'm looking at it now and I've thought about it all these days—there was no decay on him.

00:08:54.826 --> 00:08:55.736
He was not dying.

00:08:55.736 --> 00:08:58.862
That did not happen until after they bit the fruit.

00:08:58.862 --> 00:09:04.160
He was in a body that renewed itself and it was perfect.

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:19.760
So he was there and he was communicating to this big lizard-like looking dinosaur thing that was like a Jurassic Park massive long-neck looking dinosaur and he was communicating to this dinosaur.

00:09:23.746 --> 00:09:33.307
I could see him pointing his finger at this dinosaur and the dinosaur was looking down and was understanding what he was saying.

00:09:33.307 --> 00:09:37.260
Kind of like how we talk to our dogs or our cats or whatever.

00:09:37.260 --> 00:09:43.160
He was communicating to this massive dinosaur and it was looking down at him.

00:09:43.160 --> 00:09:51.976
And people say, "Well, I didn't think prehistoric ages were in the earth at that time or whatever, and dinosaurs and T-Rexes and all that stuff.

00:09:51.976 --> 00:09:56.610
" Well, this lizard thing was—and I did not see any other dinosaurs.

00:09:56.610 --> 00:10:06.045
I just saw one thing—and that dinosaur was bending down and he was eating grass and leaves off the trees.

00:10:06.045 --> 00:10:12.319
But I noticed this: there was no death in the garden of trees.

00:10:12.319 --> 00:10:16.549
The trees were not deteriorating with old dead limbs.

00:10:16.549 --> 00:10:20.777
The leaves were not turning any kind of dead-looking colors.

00:10:20.777 --> 00:10:22.765
They were all perfect.

00:10:22.765 --> 00:10:28.737
There was nothing dying at all in the garden.

00:10:28.737 --> 00:10:30.217
Everything was amazing.

00:10:30.217 --> 00:10:34.320
The trees were not like these little—we have trees where we go, "Wow, those are big trees.

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:42.960
" No, these trees that I saw in the garden, you couldn't put your arms around them.

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:46.800
They were ginormous trees, and they were huge.

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:48.700
They went so high up.

00:10:48.700 --> 00:10:55.920
They were not like the little trees that we see now; if they're 50 stories high, they're massive.

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:09.973
A redwood is huge—that's the biggest tree we know—but these trees were so huge, and there was no death in them.

00:11:10.267 --> 00:11:13.051
All the grass and the foliage was just beautiful.

00:11:13.051 --> 00:11:21.715
But this is what I noticed the most in this part of the vision that the Lord allowed me to see: the sky was alive.

00:11:23.615 --> 00:11:31.831
The atmosphere of the earth was alive, and it had a vibration to it; it was vibrating.

00:11:37.458 --> 00:11:41.440
I could feel it in the spirit when I was looking into it.

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:49.525
What the Lord allowed me to feel was the energy, the vibration of the atmosphere above the Earth's canopy.

00:11:49.890 --> 00:12:01.110
It wasn't blue like it is right now; it was like our sunsets where you see pinks and oranges and all kinds of things.

00:12:01.110 --> 00:12:03.627
That's the way the canopy looked.

00:12:03.627 --> 00:12:09.959
It had a life to it; it was almost like a fog, but it wasn't a fog.

00:12:10.335 --> 00:12:15.600
It was like thick water.

00:12:15.600 --> 00:12:23.977
I don't know how else to say this, folks; it looked like water above the atmosphere.

00:12:25.229 --> 00:12:26.840
It was all beautiful.

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:30.669
It was thick-looking, almost like a transparent, translucent atmosphere.

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:45.200
It was like a slime, but I don't know how to say it because there was no structure to it; it wasn't a solid, but it was thick, like moisture.

00:12:45.200 --> 00:12:49.466
There is no way to describe it with words.

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:01.314
You could see the stars through it.

00:13:01.314 --> 00:13:06.331
I could see lights through it, and you could see pinks and purples.

00:13:06.628 --> 00:13:07.519
It was beautiful.

00:13:09.013 --> 00:13:13.280
It was like the sun was shining off of it, making it alive and moving.

00:13:13.627 --> 00:13:19.893
Then I could see the birds, and these were birds that are not here anymore.

00:13:19.893 --> 00:13:30.347
There were different kinds of birds with massive wingspans flying around in the atmosphere in the garden.

00:13:30.347 --> 00:13:31.993
It was beautiful.

00:13:31.993 --> 00:13:39.069
The water that the dinosaur was drinking was clear and crystal, and there was no pollution.

00:13:42.100 --> 00:13:44.680
Then he takes me to another span of time.

00:13:49.168 --> 00:13:51.742
He said, "I'm going to show you the key mile markers in the timeframe of humanity.

00:14:02.600 --> 00:14:02.980
" Then he showed me Noah building the ark.

00:14:05.804 --> 00:14:06.293
I noticed his nose.

00:14:17.680 --> 00:14:25.845
There was a man with a massive white beard, but his nose was ginormous.

00:14:25.845 --> 00:14:30.959
It sounds weird, but his nose was huge.

00:14:32.111 --> 00:14:39.460
He had gray hair, and he looked like he had a hat on, like in Lord of the Rings.

00:14:40.949 --> 00:14:45.427
The people around him were all dark-looking and evil.

00:14:46.613 --> 00:14:50.949
Their countenances were dirty, like real dirt or grease.

00:14:58.366 --> 00:15:00.140
There were people behind him, and the Lord showed me this one man very clearly, with a big nose and body features.

00:15:01.520 --> 00:15:06.733
I could see the ark, and it was in a garden-type scenario; everything around it was really big, green, and beautiful.

00:15:14.024 --> 00:15:14.340
I didn't see a lot of things that looked bad.

00:15:23.669 --> 00:15:24.079
I know Eve had eaten the fruit by then, but the earth didn't look deteriorated from what I could see.

00:15:29.529 --> 00:15:31.016
Then he takes me to another part of time, and I see the pyramids and the Sphinx being built.

00:15:31.016 --> 00:15:36.730
They were using wood, ramps, pulleys, and all kinds of things to build these monuments.

00:15:43.767 --> 00:15:44.174
I didn't see any giants; I saw men working, like the Egyptians.

00:15:44.174 --> 00:15:52.354
Then he takes me to another timeframe, and I see the Roman Colosseum and the great Pantheon being built.

00:15:52.354 --> 00:15:58.880
I could see it being built like Legos, moving in front of my face.

00:16:11.840 --> 00:16:12.160
I could see Caesar Augustus, the Roman emperor, with a white robe and a laurel wreath on his head, watching over things.

00:16:24.420 --> 00:16:24.830
The history of the Roman emperors was being fast-forwarded in front of me.

00:16:26.060 --> 00:16:35.279
Then the Lord allowed me to see the Great Wall of China being built, stretching out over Asia.

00:16:46.140 --> 00:16:46.320
I saw wars happening, thousands of years of time passing in seconds.

00:16:52.000 --> 00:16:52.320
I could slow it down in the spirit realm, taking glimpses like photos.

00:16:55.260 --> 00:17:00.919
The Lord showed me Asian men riding horseback, fighting wars with swords, bows, arrows, and spears.

00:17:00.919 --> 00:17:03.120
They looked like samurai warriors.

00:17:03.120 --> 00:17:08.493
Then the Lord showed me Christopher Columbus sailing across the ocean to discover America.

00:17:10.450 --> 00:17:12.222
I could see him on the ship; he had long hair.

00:17:22.685 --> 00:17:23.090
Then he showed me World War I and World War II, and the acceleration of war.

00:17:23.090 --> 00:17:35.223
The birthing pains started in the early 1900s, and knowledge has increased with flight, jets, cars, electricity, and telecommunications, just as promised in the Bible.

00:17:35.223 --> 00:17:39.529
Then he stopped and said, "This is where you are right now.

00:17:39.529 --> 00:17:41.920
Adam's lease is up.

00:17:41.920 --> 00:17:45.394
Satan knows when Adam's lease is up.

00:17:45.394 --> 00:17:48.250
Son, it will happen on Rosh Hashanah.

00:17:48.250 --> 00:17:51.380
That's when the lease will be up.

00:18:02.411 --> 00:18:02.834
" And I saw Satan moving like a snake throughout the earth.

00:18:02.834 --> 00:18:11.267
He went to talk to the pope and was communicating to key figures in the earth and Europe, which I don't understand.

00:18:16.559 --> 00:18:27.600
Like I said in this last video, I don't understand why he wasn't trying to communicate to people in America, but he was in Europe and in the Middle East talking to the key figures.

00:18:37.310 --> 00:18:37.660
And I've told you who I believe the Antichrist is: MBS.

00:18:37.660 --> 00:18:42.159
It's just who I believe I've seen as MBS.

00:18:42.159 --> 00:18:52.920
So, all that to say this, the Lord said, "Brandon, the devil was saying, 'You've got to give me my time now.

00:18:52.920 --> 00:19:03.422
Adam's lease is over, and you've got to give me my time to do my seven years of tribulation.

00:19:03.422 --> 00:19:05.579
'" And he was petitioning.

00:19:07.884 --> 00:19:10.382
And I heard the Lord say, "I have never been defeated.

00:19:10.382 --> 00:19:13.440
I will not be defeated now.

00:19:13.440 --> 00:19:15.977
I can control time.

00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:23.200
" And he was telling Satan basically to go take a hike.

00:19:23.200 --> 00:19:24.480
"I'm controlling time.

00:19:24.480 --> 00:19:28.320
A day is a thousand years unto me.

00:19:30.688 --> 00:19:39.679
" And he said, "And I can take a sliver of this time right here.

00:19:40.066 --> 00:19:44.490
" And it was just like a little fraction, like a hair.

00:19:56.304 --> 00:19:56.509
You pull a hair out—well, not on my head—but you pull a hair out and you would be able to stretch it out.

00:20:00.945 --> 00:20:06.651
And that's how much of a sliver of time we had left to get a revival done.

00:20:06.651 --> 00:20:12.676
It was like the thickness of a hair—that thin.

00:20:12.676 --> 00:20:16.509
But he said, "That's all I need, Brandon.

00:20:16.509 --> 00:20:19.129
That's all I need.

00:20:24.188 --> 00:20:25.292
" He said, "A great revival can happen in that sliver of a time.

00:20:26.473 --> 00:20:34.846
And we will have a great massive harvest of souls, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:20:34.846 --> 00:20:40.008
" Well, I told you the angel armies were coming out of heaven to help us.

00:20:40.008 --> 00:20:47.450
But this is where it was: He no longer had to move in this time frame.

00:20:47.450 --> 00:20:58.520
When this happens, he no longer has to move through Adam's lease.

00:20:58.520 --> 00:21:10.246
Adam gave the earth to the son of man, but Adam committed high treason, messed up, and gave it to the devil.

00:21:10.246 --> 00:21:27.490
Then Jesus took it back, but it was still a lease—a covenant, I guess is what I want to call it, with man—that he would be able to reign for 6,000 years.

00:21:27.490 --> 00:21:33.867
When that time frame is over, we go into the thousand-year reign with Jesus Christ.

00:21:33.867 --> 00:21:37.200
So God had made that with man.

00:21:42.951 --> 00:21:46.847
And when that time frame is up, there will be a glory because the Lord said to me, "Brandon, people only see two sides of me and I'm multifaceted.

00:21:46.847 --> 00:21:53.848
They see the grace and they see the judgment, but I'm much more than that.

00:21:53.848 --> 00:22:00.080
" There was a deepness to the Lord that people don't understand.

00:22:04.224 --> 00:22:18.284
And he said, "Brandon, I'm going to do so much in that little sliver of time, the outpouring there's going to be—whether that is a year, two years, or three years, I don't know.

00:22:18.284 --> 00:22:29.529
" All I know is the glorious outpouring, the glorious church that he moves through unhindered by Adam's lease, will be something to be seen.

00:22:29.529 --> 00:22:34.978
We've never seen it before because all we've known is Adam's lease for 6,000 years.

00:22:37.919 --> 00:22:39.992
But we're going to see a side of God that we've never seen before.

00:22:55.039 --> 00:23:03.830
The great wells of revival, the great healing ministries that we saw in the early 1900s with Jack Coe, A.

00:23:20.248 --> 00:23:20.559
A.

00:23:20.559 --> 00:23:26.289
Allen, Smith Wigglesworth, William Branham, all the greats, Kathryn Kuhlman, all of them.

00:23:26.289 --> 00:23:39.714
We've only touched the very top surface, but we're about to see one of the greatest moves of God this planet has ever seen in a matter of just that much time.

00:23:39.714 --> 00:23:44.380
It's going to be a quick work.

00:23:52.983 --> 00:23:53.573
But Jesus is about to show us who he really is in this earth and in his body.

00:23:53.573 --> 00:24:03.520
And all the seeds that we've sowed in the past, I'm telling you, will come to harvest at last.

00:24:19.029 --> 00:24:19.259
We're going to see a great transfer of wealth from the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:24:35.616 --> 00:24:35.928
And we're going to see a great harvest of souls and great healings and demonstrations manifest.

00:24:35.928 --> 00:24:41.579
God's going to show himself real to the Jews and to his church.

00:24:47.188 --> 00:24:47.440
And I'm telling you, your unsaved loved ones are coming home.

00:24:57.867 --> 00:25:04.479
Your unsaved loved ones are coming to Jesus Christ.

00:25:04.479 --> 00:25:05.599
It's time.

00:25:05.599 --> 00:25:14.187
They will, if you petition and pray for them—I'm telling you—they will come to the saving knowledge of Jesus Christ.

00:25:14.187 --> 00:25:22.400
There will be a move of God, and it will be such that people are just going to have to flatly put their head in the sand if they don't want to see what's about to happen.

00:25:22.400 --> 00:25:30.570
Yes, there's darkness and yes, there's wars and rumors of wars, but the body of Christ is going to move as an army and you're going to see it.

00:25:30.570 --> 00:25:34.182
I believe with all my heart and we're right there.

00:25:34.182 --> 00:25:49.387
Whether it happens today and we're stepping over into it or we start to see it—he shows me when you're looking in the spirit it looks like it's right on top of you, like it's going to happen tomorrow.

00:25:51.639 --> 00:26:02.000
But there's a depth perception when you're looking in the spirit, and so sometimes that could be a five-year window, a two-day thing, or whatever.

00:26:02.000 --> 00:26:10.779
I don't try to put a time frame on the Holy Spirit in visions anymore because it gets you in trouble.

00:26:11.279 --> 00:26:16.766
Like I said, you're looking in the spirit and it looks like it's right there, but there's depth perception.

00:26:16.766 --> 00:26:29.146
So, I'm learning, and it's a part of growing on my part, knowing that what seems imminent on your time could be a year from now or it could be right now.

00:26:32.377 --> 00:26:33.736
